  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*quantum determinant*)\nClearAll[qdetT];\nqdetT[λ1_,λ2_][u_]:=T[λ1,λ2][1,1][u].T[λ1,λ2][2,2][u-h]-T[λ1,λ2][2,1][u].T[λ1,λ2][1,2][u-h];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Fusion/Hirota hierarchy for the two-site transfer matrices t2[λ1,λ2][1,s][u], built exactly as in the L=1 case (t2[λ1,λ2][2,1][u]=χ2 qdetT[λ1,λ2][u], then Hirota recursion t2[1,s][u]=t2[1,s-1][u].t2[1,1][u+(s-1)h]-t2[2,1][u+(s-1)h].t2[1,s-2][u]), with boundary conditions t2[0,s]=t2[a,0]=identity on V_λ1⊗V_λ2.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*fused transfer matrices*)\nt2[λ1_,λ2_][0,s_][u_]:=IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ1,0}]*dim[{λ2,0}]];\nt2[λ1_,λ2_][a_,0][u_]:=IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ1,0}]*dim[{λ2,0}]];\nt2[λ1_,λ2_][2,1][u_]:=χ2 qdetT[λ1,λ2][u];\nt2[λ1_,λ2_][1,s_/;s>1][u_]:=t2[λ1,λ2][1,s-1][u].t2[λ1,λ2][1,1][u+(s-1)h]-t2[λ1,λ2][2,1][u+(s-1)h].t2[λ1,λ2][1,s-2][u];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Qθ-type factors for the two sites*)\nClearAll[Qθ1,Qθ];\nQθ1[u_]:=(u-θ1);\nQθ[u_]:=(u-θ1)(u-θ2);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*SoV B-operator for L=2: the bare (1,1) monodromy element (no G, no trace) — same convention as B[λ][u]=L[λ][1,1][u-θ] at L=1.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[B2];\nB2[λ1_,λ2_][u_]:=T[λ1,λ2][1,1][u];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Step 8: SoV pseudovacuum for L=2 as the tensor product of the two single-site lowest-weight covectors.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[xSingle,x2];\nxSingle[λ_][{0}]:={Table[KroneckerDelta[ii,dim[{λ,0}]],{ii,1,dim[{λ,0}]}]};\nx2[λ1_,λ2_][{0,0}]:=KroneckerProduct[xSingle[λ1][{0}],xSingle[λ2][{0}]];\n\nx2[λ1_,λ2_][{s1_,s2_}] := x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,s2}] = x2[λ1,λ2][{0,0}].t2[λ1,λ2][1,s1][θ1].t2[λ1,λ2][1,s2][θ2]/(Product[Qθ[θ1 + (-λ1 + k - 1) h], {k, 1, s1}] Product[Qθ[θ2 + (-λ2 + k - 1) h], {k, 1, s2}]);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*checking x2 diagonalizes B*)\nTable[Table[x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,s2}].B2[λ1,λ2][u]-(u-θ1-h s1)(u-θ2-h s2)x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,s2}],{s1,0,λ1},{s2,0,λ2}],{λ1,1,3},{λ2,1,3}]//ExpandAll//Chop[#,10^(-20)]&//Flatten//Union",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352966\" data-output-id=\"7\" data-out-n=\"64\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"25\" data-sub-start=\"1\" data-sub-end=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[64]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrncuby6-wbclsi6\" data-page-width-em=\"22\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezBccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
