  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Section C — FSoV scalar product / orthogonality check. mu/Nn/nn/br/det ported verbatim from\n  Experiments/FSoV_L2.wb (that file's own cells 0-4): mu is the FSoV measure per site (supported\n  on that site's θ-tower), br is the bracket pairing (residue sum of f·mu over a site's poles),\n  det is the 2x2 Wronskian-type determinant built from br[f] and br[u f] at both sites. For\n  f=Q_A(u)Q_B(u), det[λ1,λ2][f] is the SoV scalar product <Q_A,Q_B>: it must vanish for A≠B and\n  be nonzero for A=B. See docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-16-fsov-scalar-product-design.md.*)",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*FSoV measures*)\nClearAll[mu];\nmu[λ1_,λ2_][1][u_]:=Nn[λ1,λ2][1]/(Product[(u-θ1-h k),{k,0,λ1}]Product[(u-θ2-h k),{k,0,λ2}])(1-Exp[2 π I/h (u-θ2)]);\nmu[λ1_,λ2_][2][u_]:=Nn[λ1,λ2][2]/(Product[(u-θ1-h k),{k,0,λ1}]Product[(u-θ2-h k),{k,0,λ2}])(1-Exp[2 π I/h (u-θ1)]);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Normalization factors in measure*)\nNn[λ1_,λ2_][1]:=1/(2 π I)/(1-Exp[2 π I/h(θ1-θ2)]) nn[λ1,λ2][1];\nNn[λ1_,λ2_][2]:=1/(2 π I)/(1-Exp[2 π I/h(θ2-θ1)]) nn[λ1,λ2][2];\n\nnn[λ1_,λ2_][1]:= (-1)^(λ1+λ2-1)h^(λ1)Gamma[λ1+1] Product[θ2+k h-θ1,{k,0,λ2}]//Simplify;\nnn[λ1_,λ2_][2]:= (-1)^(λ1+λ2-1)h^(λ2)Gamma[λ2+1] Product[θ1+k h-θ2,{k,0,λ1}]//Simplify;",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*brackets of function f, given by contour integral around all poles in measure*)\nClearAll[br];\nbr[λ1_,λ2_][1][f_]:=2 π I Plus@@(Residue[f mu[λ1,λ2][1][u],{u,#}]&/@Table[θ1+h k,{k,0,λ1}])//Expand//Simplify;\nbr[λ1_,λ2_][2][f_]:=2 π I Plus@@(Residue[f mu[λ1,λ2][2][u],{u,#}]&/@Table[θ2+h k,{k,0,λ2}])//Expand//Simplify;",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[det];\ndet[λ1_,λ2_][f_]:=1/(f/.u:>θ1)/(f/.u:>θ2)/(θ2-θ1)({{br[λ1,λ2][1][f],br[λ1,λ2][1][u f]},{br[λ1,λ2][2][f],br[λ1,λ2][2][u f]}}//Det//Expand//Simplify)",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Port-fidelity check: fsovL2CachedFormula is FSoV_L2.wb's own cached Out[215] for\n  det[1,1][f[u] z^(u/h)], transcribed verbatim with θ1,θ2,h,z,f still symbolic (as they were in\n  that standalone notebook). Here θ1,θ2,h are already bound (cell 0), so comparing the freshly\n  computed det[...] against this formula with the SAME substitution applied is a direct\n  transcription check, independent of re-deriving the algebra.*)\nClearAll[fsovL2CachedFormula];\nfsovL2CachedFormula[θ1_,θ2_,h_,z_,fn_] := -(z^((θ1+θ2)/h-θ1/h-θ2/h) (z fn[h+θ1] (fn[θ2] (h-θ1+θ2)+z (θ1-θ2) fn[h+θ2])+fn[θ1] (fn[θ2] (θ1-θ2)-z fn[h+θ2] (h+θ1-θ2))))/(fn[θ1] fn[θ2] (θ2-θ1));\nportCheckDiff = Simplify[det[1,1][f[u] z^(u/h)] - fsovL2CachedFormula[θ1,θ2,h,z,f]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352966\" data-output-id=\"15\" data-out-n=\"120\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"39\" data-sub-start=\"7\" data-sub-end=\"7\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[120]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrncunfm-4zc41nv\" data-page-width-em=\"22\" data-latex-b64=\"MA==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[120]= 0",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "07d0038f-921c-4f74-be8f-041babc6abd5"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*statesOf: the sorted {M,n} key list for a representation, read off TauEigensystem's memoized\n  cache (built once in Section B) rather than re-deriving dPred here.\n  GramMatrix: the full Gram matrix G_{(M,n),(M',n')} = det[λ1,λ2][Q1(M,n)(u) Q1(M',n')(u)] over\n  ALL states of the representation at once — this covers same-M degeneracy AND cross-M pairs in\n  a single object, per the design.*)\nClearAll[statesOf, GramMatrix];\nstatesOf[λ1_,λ2_] := SortBy[Keys[TauEigensystem[λ1,λ2]], {First,Last}];\nGramMatrix[λ1_,λ2_] := Module[{s = statesOf[λ1,λ2]},\n  Table[\n    det[λ1,λ2][Q1[λ1,λ2][s1[[1]],s1[[2]]][u] Q1[λ1,λ2][s2[[1]],s2[[2]]][u]],\n    {s1, s}, {s2, s}]\n];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "states21 = statesOf[2, 1]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
