n class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Indeterminate</span></span><span class=\"mclose\">∣</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:-0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">⟩</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
